news Feed System:

HLD - Requirements

Functional Requirements:

1. System should be able to display posts and see friend's post on feed page.
2. System should be able to have criteria for display news - reverse chronological order
3. Should support images/videos.

Non Functional Requirements:

1. Consistent
2. Scalable
3. Durability

Back of the envelope estimations:

1. MAU : 1 billion
2. DAU : 50 percent of 1 billion
3. 500 million -- users per day
4. 500 million users * 4 posts per day = 2000 million posts per day
5. posts per sec = 2000 million posts per day = 20000 posts per sec
6. Each post size avg = 500 KB  * 20000 posts per sec = 10 GB/sec
7. year = 10 GB * 365 * 86400 = 315PB


